title: Ground Turkey Sweet Potato Skillet
directions: Heat coconut oil in a skillet over medium high heat.
Add ground turkey and minced garlic. Cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.
Add diced onions and diced peppers, and cook until onions are golden brown.
Add diced sweet potato, cover skillet, and cook until tender, stirring occasionally.
ingredients: 1 tbs. coconut oil, raw, extra-virgin, organic
1/2 lbs. turkey, ground, grass-fed or pastured, organic
1/4 c. bell pepper, red, fresh, organic
sea salt, unrefined, & fresh ground pepper, organic to taste
